  07 Dec 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  openbox-themes-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword as per bug #156873. Thanks to Mark Kowarsky
  (mark_alec) for reporting.

  14 Jun 2006; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  openbox-themes-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  24 Aug 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  openbox-themes-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  FreeBSD fixes: cp -a -> cp -pPR.

  01 Aug 2005; Leonardo Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org>
  openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild, openbox-themes-0.6.ebuild,
  openbox-themes-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Modified gtk-engines-thinice dependency to gtk-engines, since the latter
  provides the ThinIce engine now, and >=x11-themes/gtk-engines-thinice-2 is
  being deprecated.

*openbox-themes-0.6-r1 (03 Jan 2005)

  03 Jan 2005; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +openbox-themes-0.6-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bumping, including a workaround from bug 50985. Thanks to John Ross
  Hunt <john.ross.hunt@comcast.net> for reporting. Also, changing the gnome
  IUSE to gtk IUSE. Change DEPEND to RDEPEND.

  06 May 2004; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> -openbox-themes-0.2.ebuild,
  openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild, openbox-themes-0.6.ebuild:
  Remove explicit S=

  06 May 2004; Ciaran McCreesh <ciaranm@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.6.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc, #50234

*openbox-themes-0.6 (04 Apr 2004)

  04 Apr 2004; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.6.ebuild:
  Rolled a new version.

  24 Jan 2004; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Update homepage.

  24 Jan 2004; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Add depend on gtk-engines-thinice if USE="gnome", as the gtk themes included
  in this package use the engine.

  14 Dec 2003; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Masked stable on ppc

  06 Dec 2003; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.2.ebuild,
  openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Marking stable on x86.

*openbox-themes-0.5-r1 (18 Nov 2003)

  18 Nov 2003; Brandon Low <lostlogic@gentoo.org>
  openbox-themes-0.5-r1.ebuild, openbox-themes-0.5.ebuild:
  Fix the install path so that openbox can actually use the themes

*openbox-themes-0.5 (16 Nov 2003)

  16 Nov 2003; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> openbox-themes-0.2.ebuild,
  openbox-themes-0.5.ebuild:
  New version, adds some new themes, notably a port of Rephorm's Winter. Also
  removes some themes which are unfinished, and a few which are now includedin
  the default Openbox ebuild. Fixed headers.

  14 Oct 2003; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> :
  Cleaning up in here, thanks for the qa msterret.

*openbox-themes-0.2 (13 Oct 2003)

  22 Sep 2003; Brandon Hale <tseng@gentoo.org> :
  Adds a few new themes, and updates for openbox beta4 ;)

